[[File:Uitreiking van de Staatsprijs voor Letterkunde in het Muiderslot Weeknummer 54-22 - Open Beelden - 30893.ogv|thumb|thumbtime=0:52|Laudatio by De Waal (film, 1954)]] '''Anna de Waal''' (25 November 1906, [[Culemborg]] – 22 March 1981, [[Arnhem]]), was a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] politician (Catholic party). She was state secretary of education in 1953–1957. De Waal was the first female government secretary or minister in the Netherlands.
