hn Beswick (politician)|John Beswick]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia (Tasmanian Division)|Liberal]] || 18 February 1992 || 18 March 1996 |- bgcolor="#DDEEFF" | [[Sue Napier]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia (Tasmanian Division)|Liberal]] || 18 March 1996 || 14 September 1998 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[Paul Lennon]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 14 September 1998 || 21 March 2004 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[David Llewellyn (Australian politician)|David Llewellyn]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 22 March 2004 || 5 April 2006 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[Bryan Green]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 5 April 2006 || 15 July 2006 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[Steve Kons]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 30 October 2006 || 9 April 2008 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[David Bartlett]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 10 April 2008 || 26 May 2008 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[Lara Giddings]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 26 May 2008 || 24 January 2011 |- bgcolor="#FFE8E8" | [[Bryan Green]] || [[Australian Labor Party (Tasmanian Branch)|Labor]] || 24 January 2011 || 31 March 2014 |- bgcolor="#DDEEFF" | [[Jeremy Rockliff]] || [[Liberal Party of Australia (Tasmanian Division)|Liberal]] || 31 March 2014 || present |}
