[[File:Hengchun-Township Taiwan Southernmost-Point-of-Taiwan-01.jpg|thumb|Taiwan Southernmost Point marker]]
[[File:Southernmost-point.jpg|thumb|Sign leading to the point]]

'''Taiwan Southernmost Point''' ({{zh|c=台灣最南點|p=Táiwān Zuì Nán Diǎn}}) is the southernmost point of [[Taiwan]] located in [[Kenting National Park]], [[Hengchun|Hengchun Township]], [[Pingtung County]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tripadvisor.com/LocationPhotoDirectLink-g297909-d553564-i18640577-Kenting_National_Park-Pingtung.html|title=Taiwan's southernmost point in Kenting National Park - Picture of Kenting National Park, Pingtung|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rtaiwanr.com/kenting/the-southernmost-point-in-taiwan|title=Taiwan Southernmost Point - roundTAIWANround|author=roundTAIWANround|work=roundTAIWANround}}</ref>

